Corporate Data










We are helping improve the quality of life and enabling people to realize their dreams by providing added-value information, technology and services in the electronics field.
Based on a partnership with a number of domestic and overseas manufacturers, Vitec group has contributed to the realization of superior products in a variety of fields.
As symbolized by the name of our company (Value Integrated Technology), we will continue working hard and drawing upon the full capabilities of our entire group to meet and exceed the expectations and diverse needs of our customers as a comprehensive electronics trading company. This will be made possible by utilizing the superior abilities of our personnel to provide high added-value information services.









