VITEC GLOBAL ELECTRONICS CO., LTD.







VITEC GLOBAL ELECTRONICS CO., LTD.


We offers a broad lineup of products that address various customer needs. We thus handle a wide variety of semiconductor products, electronic devices and measurement instruments selected from around the world.
Going beyond simple product introductions, our mission is to fulfill all the needs of our customers, whether they are for solutions, technological development support, or ODM. As a total business coordinator, We aims to create new businesses and schemes with the aim of developing high-value-added businesses.
The products that we handle are used in a diverse range of industries, from consumer electronics to automobiles, and industrial machinery to infrastructure. We are also keen on entering promising growth fields such as IoT(Internet of Things) Business. We will strive to strengthen our business relationships with affiliates and partners inside and outside Japan, enhance local businesses in Asia, Europe and the U.S. and build overseas business on a Group-wide basis.







Established
May 1st, 2015


Address
