Product Information>
Solutions and Support Business







In the Solutions and Support Business, Vitec is working diligently to further strengthen its sales and marketing activities while maintaining a keen eye on the trends of each era and market. In our ODM/OEM (design and manufacturing contract) activities, we are focusing mainly on TV board, BMS and other modules as well as finished products (in-vehicle, digital broadcasting-related, environmental, digital camera and other products) that offer new and additional value.
          In addition, we put forward optimal solutions in such areas as technical support (software/IP), contract purchasing and logistics that accurately address the needs of customers.







Inquiries

          For inquiries relating to the Technology Proposal-Based Business please contact the following:
          1st Sales Division, Sales Department1
          Vitec Co., Ltd.
          TEL.: +81-3-3458-4616
          E-MAIL: info@vitec.co.jp





